<br>
Well, firstly, this is the Soapbox. Do not come into the Soapbox if you have reservations about reading flames. This is the purpose of the Soapbox. And if you don't like it, and don't come here, don't write off other people entirely just because they're using it for it's intended purpose.<br>
<br>
Also, as long as the people using this server, and less so, the people using this server's board, remain the same, we aren't becoming a blue server with a special ruleset. What makes FV FV isn't the players choosing to call another a &quot;troubled and confused player who should think twice before taking my mob again&quot; versus &quot;an incest-born fuckface with a needledick and a fancy for little kids motherfucking KSer.&quot; The latter flame might give you insight into the emotional maturity of that flamer in particular, but it has zero bearing on the quality of FV.<br>
<br>
IMO, what it comes down to is the players and the way they play, not what the players write on a flameboard when they're mad.<br>
<br>
So come on, stop with this nonsense. Your words can be gentle if you'd like, but again, it has zero bearing on the quality of the server. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=thraallfv>ThraallFV</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 549<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(5/20/03 11:52 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm49.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=37.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.calpoly.edu/~msamuel/frgSthrl.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: FV lost</span><hr size=1> I found FV, its about the 3rd from top on the server select screen.<br>
